responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "13A604974FB3501BF7A2799E0EA81629", "His name\'s Carlin Boyle. The last time I saw him he was boasting about something, as he often does. He said he\'d already been on the fairgrounds. You think it might be where he got in trouble? Maybe he went back there to prove his story. I knew we shouldn\'t have given him such a hard time.")
